    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/275a2279b4d873b409d4ef2dc33a4768.poster.avif?t=1766137662\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/275a2279b4d873b409d4ef2dc33a4768.webm?t=1766137662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/275a2279b4d873b409d4ef2dc33a4768.mp4?t=1766137662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grab and Guts是一款惊心动魄的射击游戏，带您与JuraPis一起穿越人体，微观世界和其他难以想象的领域进行非凡的旅程。 装备一个抓钩，你将导航复杂的路径，进入重要的开口，并收集强大的武器。 你的任务是惩罚可怕的寄生虫-在生物上茁壮成长的恶心苍蝇-并让他们明白他们的位置在坟墓里。 作为生活世界的代表，这取决于你来净化这些出没的世界，恢复平衡<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/21ec54033b5f0f52499e27695e9114c8.poster.avif?t=1766137662\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/21ec54033b5f0f52499e27695e9114c8.webm?t=1766137662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113780/extras/21ec54033b5f0f52499e27695e9114c8.mp4?t=1766137662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要特点:</strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的环境:探索人体,微观领域,和超越.<br></li><li>抓钩力学：使用你的抓钩导航复杂的路径和到达基本区域。<br></li><li>武器收集：收集各种武器来对抗寄生入侵者。<br></li><li>挑战敌人：面对寄生苍蝇和其他怪诞生物。<br></li><li>英雄使命：踏上保护和净化生活世界免受寄生威胁的追求。</li></ul>",
